Name: Dead territory
About the game: A computer game, a killer arcade with a top view about the battles of people against monsters. After the nuclear disaster, all living things took on a new form. Your mission: to clear the territory of the undead. And find a way to the next level. Procedurally generated levels. Several types of weapons: 1 - shotgun 2 - bazooka 3 - double-barreled gun 4 - axe Procedurally generated levels give endless adventure to 4 players.
